<div dir="ltr" style=''box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;  text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial''><br style="box-sizing: border-box"></div>
<div dir="ltr" style=''box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;  text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial''>Conforme conversado com a Priscila, solicito 10 equipamentos (kit AVL e kit rotograma) para instalação de telemetria em novos veículos.</div>
